ZH: 今天早晨出门时，外面弥漫着浓雾。
EN: There was dense fog outside when I left this morning.

ZH: 大雾使能见度变得非常低。
EN: The thick fog reduced visibility drastically.

ZH: 雾太浓了，我担心开车行驶。
EN: The fog was so dense that I was worried about driving.

ZH: 在浓雾中行走时，请注意自己的安全。
EN: Please pay attention to your safety while walking in dense fog.

ZH: 浓雾笼罩的景象让人感到诡异。
EN: The scene cloaked in dense fog was eerie.

ZH: 我在浓雾中迷了路，不知道该怎么回家。
EN: I got lost in the thick fog and didn't know how to get home.

ZH: 浓雾散去后，我们才看清楚周围的环境。
EN: We could only see the surroundings clearly after the dense fog dispersed.

ZH: 浓雾阻碍了航班的正常起降。
EN: The dense fog disrupted the normal takeoff and landing of flights.

ZH: 由于浓雾，火车的运行速度被限制了。
EN: The speed of train service was restricted due to the dense fog.

ZH: 天空被浓雾所遮蔽，太阳无法照耀下来。
EN: The sky was obscured by thick fog, and the sun couldn't shine through.

ZH: 雾气中的水分让我的衣服湿透了。
EN: The moisture in the fog soaked my clothes.

ZH: 因为浓雾的原因，航班被取消了。
EN: The flight was canceled due to the heavy fog.

ZH: 在浓雾中，听觉变得更加敏锐。
EN: In the thick fog, hearing becomes more acute.

ZH: 在这种浓雾中，很容易迷路。
EN: It's easy to get lost in this kind of dense fog.

ZH: 我们通过浓雾只能看到一小部分景象。
EN: We could only see a small part of the scenery through the dense fog.

ZH: 驾驶员应该减速行驶以适应浓雾的条件。
EN: Drivers should slow down to adapt to the conditions of dense fog.

ZH: 雾使得整个城市显得模糊不清。
EN: The fog made the entire city appear blurry.

ZH: 那艘船在浓雾中迅速消失了。
EN: The ship disappeared quickly in the dense fog.

ZH: 浓雾中的寒意使我打起了寒颤。
EN: The coldness in the dense fog made me shiver.

ZH: 行人在浓雾中变得难以辨认。
EN: Pedestrians become difficult to recognize in the dense fog.
